{"article_id":"TG4kTVwBYE7DCmo4","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Donald Trump defended Supreme Court nominee Brett Kavanaugh amid allegations of sexual assault","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"but suggested","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"he ' d be open to postponing a confirmation vote .","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"`` If it takes a little delay ,","depth":9},{"id":4,"text":"it ' ll take a little delay , ''","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"Trump told reporters at the White House Monday ,","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"adding","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"that he hadn ' t spoken to Kavanaugh that day .","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"The president also said","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"Kavanaugh is one of `` the finest people","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"I ' ve ever known . ''","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"Trump dismissed a question","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"about whether Kavanaugh offered to withdraw .","depth":5},{"id":13,"text":"Later , White House spokesman Raj Shah said in a statement","depth":4},{"id":14,"text":"that Kavanaugh was willing to testify","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"to `` clear his name of this false allegation '' as soon as Tuesday ,","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"if the Judiciary Committee is ready to hear him .","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"Trump speaks at the White House on Sept. 17 .","depth":5},{"id":18,"text":"Photographer :","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"Evan Vucci/AP","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"The woman","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"who made the accusation ,","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"Christine Blasey Ford , has also said","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"she ' s willing to testify before the Senate Judiciary Committee","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"as Republicans debate how to handle the allegations","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"that threaten to derail his confirmation .","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"The nomination is scheduled for a Thursday vote by the panel ,","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"but a growing number of Republicans suggested Monday","depth":12},{"id":28,"text":"the vote may need to be delayed .","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"Senator Roy Blunt of Missouri , a member of Senate GOP leadership , said ,","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"`` These are serious allegations","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"that need to be looked at closely by the committee","depth":13},{"id":32,"text":"before any other action is taken . \"","depth":13},{"id":33,"text":"Senator Susan Collins , a pivotal GOP vote , told reporters","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"that Kavanaugh `` emphatically denied '' the allegation","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"when she spoke with him by phone on Friday .","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"Before making a judgment ,","depth":13},{"id":37,"text":"she said ,","depth":13},{"id":38,"text":"she wants to see `` testimony under oath with a lot of questions","depth":13},{"id":39,"text":"asked of both of them . '' `","depth":13},{"id":40,"text":"` Obviously ,","depth":13},{"id":41,"text":"if Judge Kavanaugh has lied about what happened ,","depth":14},{"id":42,"text":"that would be disqualifying , ''","depth":14},{"id":43,"text":"said Collins of Maine .","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"The senator said","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"she was told that Judiciary Committee Republicans would meet Monday","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"to decide what to do .","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"Kavanaugh said Monday","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"he ' s willing to talk to the Judiciary Committee in any forum","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"to `` defend my integrity . ''","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"\" This is a completely false allegation .","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"I have never done anything like what the accuser describes","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"-- to her or to anyone , ''","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"Kavanaugh said in a statement","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"issued by the White House .","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"`` Because this never happened ,","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"I had no idea","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"who was making this accusation","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"until she identified herself yesterday . ''","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"Kavanaugh visited the White House for a meeting Monday morning ,","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"said a White House official","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"who didn ' t give further details .","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"Read More :","depth":6},{"id":63,"text":"White House Is Said Not to Ask FBI to Vet Kavanaugh Allegations","depth":6},{"id":64,"text":"The allegation puts heavy pressure on moderate senators","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"who must decide whether to vote for Kavanaugh at the risk","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"of angering the \" Me Too \" movement .","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"That growing backlash against men","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"facing claims","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"of sexually abusing women","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"has already forced the resignations of top executives and some lawmakers .","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"Collins and fellow GOP Senator Lisa Murkowski of Alaska haven ' t said","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"whether they ' ll vote to confirm Kavanaugh ,","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"nor have a handful of Democrats from states","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"that backed Trump in 2016 .","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"It ' s also a significant challenge for Republicans","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"who are struggling to win suburban women ' s votes in the Nov. 6 election","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"that will decide control of the U.S. House and Senate .","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"Prospects for a swift confirmation were put in doubt amid calls from key GOP senators and Democrats for an investigation .","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"But Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell of Kentucky , in a floor speech , backed Judiciary Chairman Chuck Grassley ' s strategy","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"of having staff interview Kavanaugh and Ford","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"instead of holding a public hearing .","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"Senate Minority Leader Chuck Schumer , a New York Democrat , said","depth":14},{"id":83,"text":"the GOP needs to call Ford before the committee ,","depth":14},{"id":84,"text":"adding ,","depth":14},{"id":85,"text":"\" What are they afraid of ?","depth":15},{"id":86,"text":"Are they afraid","depth":16},{"id":87,"text":"she might be persuasive ? \"","depth":16},{"id":88,"text":"Ford , a California university professor , is \" willing to do whatever it takes","depth":14},{"id":89,"text":"to get her story forth , \"","depth":14},{"id":90,"text":"her attorney , Debra Katz , told NBC ' s \" Today \" show .","depth":13},{"id":91,"text":"Katz told CNN in a separate interview","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"that Ford hasn ' t been contacted yet by the committee .","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"GOP Senator Orrin Hatch of Utah , a senior Judiciary Committee member and strong backer of Kavanaugh , said","depth":10},{"id":94,"text":"he spoke Monday with the nominee ,","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"who insisted","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"that he was innocent","depth":13},{"id":97,"text":"and that he wasn ' t at the party","depth":14},{"id":98,"text":"where he is accused of attacking Ford .","depth":14},{"id":99,"text":"Hatch said","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"the matter must be investigated .","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"Even if Ford ' s claim turned out to be true ,","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"`` I think","depth":14},{"id":103,"text":"it would be hard for senators not to consider who he is today , \"","depth":14},{"id":104,"text":"Hatch said .","depth":13},{"id":105,"text":"`` He has denied this","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"and I feel bad","depth":13},{"id":107,"text":"that this happened to him . \"","depth":13},{"id":108,"text":"Grassley of Iowa said in a statement Monday","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"he ' s working `` to get to the bottom of these claims \"","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"by setting up phone calls with Ford and Kavanaugh , an option","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"top committee Democrat Dianne Feinstein of California has rejected as inadequate .","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"Grassley blamed Democrats","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"for not previously disclosing the claim by Ford ,","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"who had sought to remain anonymous","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"before ultimately agreeing to be publicly identified .","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"Grassley didn ' t say","depth":8},{"id":117,"text":"whether Thursday ' s committee vote will go forward .","depth":8},{"id":118,"text":"Republicans are aiming for full Senate confirmation","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"before the Supreme Court term begins Oct. 1 .","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"The Washington Post published a detailed account from the accuser on Sunday .","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"Days earlier Kavanaugh had seemed on track for quick approval .","depth":10},{"id":122,"text":"The administration is gearing up for a counteroffensive ,","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"a White House official said .","depth":12},{"id":124,"text":"The Trump team plans to try to discredit the charges","depth":14},{"id":125,"text":"for surfacing late in the confirmation process","depth":14},{"id":126,"text":"and to question the credibility of the accuser","depth":14},{"id":127,"text":"because she didn ' t tell anybody about the incident at the time ,","depth":14},{"id":128,"text":"the official said .","depth":12},{"id":129,"text":"White House adviser Kellyanne Conway told reporters Monday","depth":14},{"id":130,"text":"that the accuser ' s allegations should be heard by the Senate .","depth":14},{"id":131,"text":"\" She should not be insulted ,","depth":16},{"id":132,"text":"she should not be ignored ,","depth":16},{"id":133,"text":"she should testify under oath","depth":16},{"id":134,"text":"and she should do it on Capitol Hill , \"","depth":16},{"id":135,"text":"Conway said .","depth":14},{"id":136,"text":"\" But that ' s up to the Senate Judiciary Committee ,","depth":14},{"id":137,"text":"they should decide the forum .","depth":14},{"id":138,"text":"And Judge Kavanaugh should also testify to these 36-year-old allegations . ''","depth":13},{"id":139,"text":"Murkowski told CNN Monday","depth":13},{"id":140,"text":"that she ' s open to a delay in the committee vote .","depth":13},{"id":141,"text":"\" If there are more questions","depth":15},{"id":142,"text":"that need to be asked and answered ,","depth":15},{"id":143,"text":"then I think","depth":15},{"id":144,"text":"it would be appropriate for that time , \"","depth":15},{"id":145,"text":"she told the network .","depth":13},{"id":146,"text":"The Post identified Ford , a 51-year-old research psychologist and professor at Palo Alto University in California , as the woman","depth":9},{"id":147,"text":"whose accusation surfaced last week","depth":10},{"id":148,"text":"and raised the first serious doubts about Kavanaugh ' s confirmation .","depth":10},{"id":149,"text":"The newspaper quoted Ford ' s detailed description of the incident ,","depth":9},{"id":150,"text":"and said","depth":10},{"id":151,"text":"it also viewed notes from a 2013 therapy session","depth":11},{"id":152,"text":"in which she had called it a \" rape attempt . \"","depth":11},{"id":153,"text":"The White House on Friday released a statement from Kavanaugh","depth":7},{"id":154,"text":"in which the nominee said ,","depth":8},{"id":155,"text":"\" I categorically and unequivocally deny this allegation .","depth":9},{"id":156,"text":"I did not do this back in high school or at any time . \"","depth":9},{"id":157,"text":"The controversy comes 27 years after the bruising confirmation of Supreme Court Justice Clarence Thomas ,","depth":8},{"id":158,"text":"who was accused of sexually harassing attorney Anita Hill at two federal jobs ,","depth":9},{"id":159,"text":"including when he chaired the U.S . Equal Employment Opportunity Commission","depth":10},{"id":160,"text":"that handles harassment and discrimination issues .","depth":10},{"id":161,"text":"Thomas was confirmed on a 52-48 vote .","depth":7},{"id":162,"text":"Sunday ' s development threatens what would be a major win for Trump ' s White House and McConnell","depth":10},{"id":163,"text":"as they seek to give a strong rightward tilt to the federal judiciary .","depth":10},{"id":164,"text":"Republicans ' 51-49 control of the Senate means","depth":11},{"id":165,"text":"they need no Democratic support","depth":12},{"id":166,"text":"to confirm Kavanaugh .","depth":12},{"id":167,"text":"Kavanaugh could provide the fifth vote","depth":12},{"id":168,"text":"to overturn the Roe v. Wade abortion-rights decision .","depth":13},{"id":169,"text":"He called Roe an \" important precedent \" during his Senate Judiciary confirmation hearing","depth":14},{"id":170,"text":"but refused to say","depth":15},{"id":171,"text":"whether the ruling was correct .","depth":15},{"id":172,"text":"Kavanaugh ' s potential impact on the abortion debate is a risk to the GOP ' s already lackluster standing with women ,","depth":12},{"id":173,"text":"and the sexual assault allegation could make things worse .","depth":12},{"id":174,"text":"Female voters preferred Democratic candidates over Republican ones by 54 percent to 33 percent ,","depth":10},{"id":175,"text":"while 62 percent of women disapproved of Trump ' s job performance ,","depth":10},{"id":176,"text":"according to an NPR/PBS NewsHour/Marist poll in July .","depth":9},{"id":177,"text":"The Post quoted Ford as saying","depth":11},{"id":178,"text":"Kavanaugh and a friend were \" stumbling drunk \"","depth":12},{"id":179,"text":"when they took her into a bedroom during a party in a house in the Maryland suburbs of Washington .","depth":12},{"id":180,"text":"Kavanaugh pinned her to the bed","depth":13},{"id":181,"text":"and groped her through her clothes ,","depth":14},{"id":182,"text":"grinding his body against hers","depth":15},{"id":183,"text":"and trying to pull off her clothes ,","depth":15},{"id":184,"text":"the Post quoted Ford as saying .","depth":12},{"id":185,"text":"She said","depth":13},{"id":186,"text":"that","depth":14},{"id":187,"text":"when she tried to scream ,","depth":15},{"id":188,"text":"he put his hand over her mouth .","depth":15},{"id":189,"text":"She said","depth":14},{"id":190,"text":"she believed","depth":15},{"id":191,"text":"the attack occurred in 1982 .","depth":15},{"id":192,"text":"\" I thought","depth":16},{"id":193,"text":"he might inadvertently kill me , \"","depth":16},{"id":194,"text":"the Post quoted Ford as saying .","depth":15},{"id":195,"text":"She said","depth":16},{"id":196,"text":"Kavanaugh ' s friend , Mark Judge , jumped on top of them ,","depth":18},{"id":197,"text":"sending them tumbling ,","depth":18},{"id":198,"text":"and she was able to escape ,","depth":17},{"id":199,"text":"the newspaper reported .","depth":15},{"id":200,"text":"She said","depth":12},{"id":201,"text":"she went home","depth":13},{"id":202,"text":"and didn ' t tell anyone","depth":14},{"id":203,"text":"until she and her husband were in couples therapy in 2012 .","depth":14},{"id":204,"text":"The Weekly Standard quoted Judge on Friday","depth":12},{"id":205,"text":"as saying","depth":13},{"id":206,"text":"no such incident ever occurred .","depth":13},{"id":207,"text":"The Post said","depth":13},{"id":208,"text":"it viewed notes from that session and an individual therapy session the following year .","depth":13},{"id":209,"text":"The paper said","depth":13},{"id":210,"text":"the 2013 notes showed","depth":14},{"id":211,"text":"that Ford described a \" rape attempt \" in her late teens .","depth":14},{"id":212,"text":"Her husband , Russell Ford , told the newspaper","depth":13},{"id":213,"text":"that","depth":15},{"id":214,"text":"when she described the incident in the 2012 session ,","depth":16},{"id":215,"text":"she used Kavanaugh ' s last name","depth":16},{"id":216,"text":"and said","depth":15},{"id":217,"text":"she was concerned","depth":16},{"id":218,"text":"he might eventually be nominated to the Supreme Court .","depth":16},{"id":219,"text":"He has been a federal appeals court judge since 2006 .","depth":12},{"id":220,"text":"Ford and Katz , her lawyer , didn ' t return calls","depth":9},{"id":221,"text":"seeking comment .","depth":9},{"id":222,"text":"- With assistance by Ben Brody , Terrence Dopp , Justin Sink , Laura Curtis , Shannon Pettypiece , and Erik Wasson","depth":1}],"relations":[{"parent":445,"left":444,"right":222,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":444,"left":239,"right":443,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":239,"left":235,"right":238,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":235,"left":233,"right":234,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":233,"left":225,"right":232,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":225,"left":0,"right":224,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":224,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":232,"left":229,"right":231,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":229,"left":227,"right":228,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":227,"left":226,"right":5,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":226,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":228,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":231,"left":8,"right":230,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":230,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":234,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":238,"left":13,"right":237,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":237,"left":236,"right":16,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":236,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":443,"left":283,"right":442,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":283,"left":241,"right":282,